name: David Ramirez
text: Lol, if it gets down to "You saw the body? You were there as a witness?" then you might as well disbelieve that anything Duterte did helped with crime and the economy, because you are demanding a fantasy level of proof, which if you applied to anything means almost nothing is believable.
